-- Obama to make statement on 'fiscal cliff' at 5 p.m
-- 
-- Fri Dec 21, 2012 4:27pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/21/us-usa-fiscal-obama-statement-idUSBRE8BK16N20121221

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - President Barack Obama will make a statement at 5 p.m. EST (2200 GMT) on Friday on the "fiscal cliff" stand-off with Republicans in Congress, the White House said. 
 (Reporting By  Matt Spetalnick ; Editing by  Sandra Maler )